featured_reviews.review_id:
Chikodi has five mosques like Pool Masjid (150 years old), Jame
Masjij (biggest), Bagwan Masjij (Syedgalli new) and Hospet Mosque.
There are dargahs ascribed to Ashavali Shah near Pool Mosque,
Khaderde, Mehboob Suhhani Baghdadi, Loten Shah Baba, Arabshah
Baba, Maulali Chilla near Prabhudevaragudi and Masab Bi. The Urns is held in Ashavali Shah Darga in the month of Ramzan.
About 4000 Muslims devotees assemble. Similarly,the urns of Mehboob
Subhani darga in the month of Zilhaj attracts more than 5000, Muslims
Q<J
and others.The place is also known for Quwali programme
